# PBR textures for the Sponza model.
# For more information: www.alexandre-pestana.com
# 
# Updated by Arthur Langereis (@zenmumbler)
# - converted to use optimized PNGs for much smaller disk size
# - using Pm / Pr notations for PBR maps/values
# - removed all the old/unused properties
# - replaced full-white/black textures with single values
# - removed redundant normal maps for fabrics
# - shrunk ChainTexture_metallic to 512x512
# - use norm instead of bump for normal maps
# - disable normal maps as they are no good

